name: dead_lucky
description:
...You've got to ask yourself one question: Do I feel lucky?..
This piece was hand-drawn (with mouse and stylus) and animated using Aseprite. Its seamless loop consists of 100's of layers, and 120 frames. Each frame lasts 42 milliseconds. The colors are derived from the PICO-8 palette and opacity blending. 576x768.
